https://w3id.org/babelon/comment.value: label of HP:0031761 (Infantile constant esotropia)  ; abnormality of the eye

value.value: 6 aydan önce meydana gelen sabit ezotropi. Tipik olarak geniş bir sapma açısı, değişken sabitleme (bu yüzden düşük ambiliyopi riski) ve binoküler tek görüş için zayıf potansiyel ile ilişkilidir. İnfantil (sabit) ezotropili bireylerde geç nistagmus veya belirgin geç nistagmus, ayrışmış dikey ıraksaklık, siklotropiya, anormal baş pozisyonu, sınırlı abdüksiyon dahil diğer özellikler mevcut olabilir

https://w3id.org/babelon/source_value.value: Constant esotropia occurring before 6 months of age. It is typically associated with a large angle of deviation, alternating fixation (therefore low risk of amblyopia) and poor potential for binocular single vision. Other features that might be present in individuals with infantile (constant) esotropia include latent nystagmus or manifest latent nystagmus, dissociated vertical divergence, cyclotropia, abnormal head posture, limited abduction.

value.value: Constant esotropia occurring before 6 months of age. Other features that might be present in individuals with infantile (constant) esotropia include latent nystagmus or manifest latent nystagmus, dissociated vertical divergence, cyclotropia, abnormal head posture, limited abduction.

Trvalá esotropie, která se objevuje před 6. měsícem věku. Typicky je spojena s velkým úhlem deviace, střídavou fixací (tedy nízkým rizikem amblyopie) a slabým potenciálem pro binokulární jednoduché vidění. Mezi další znaky, které mohou být přítomny u jedinců s infantilní (konstantní) esotropií, patří latentní nystagmus nebo manifestní latentní nystagmus, disociovaná vertikální divergence, cyklotropie, abnormální držení hlavy, omezená abdukce.
